parameters:
"Alright, the bell has rung, so let's take attendance. First
up... Asahi... Huh? Asahi Makoto?"

"Oh, it's rare for Asahi to be late. Well, I've just started
taking attendance, so I'll let it slide this time."

(It's rare for Makoto to be late. But I'm glad it's not a
cold. Today's the day... Today's the day I'll apologize to
her.)

"Hey, hey, don't space out this early in the morning. You
won't last the day—? Alright, next—. Shimizu—"

However, the chance to talk to Makoto didn't come as
expected, and before I knew it, the day was over and I
hadn't accomplished anything. But I didn't give up, and
decided to follow Makoto on her way home.
"Uh, if X is Z and Y is the dragon and..."
(What kind of problem is he solving?)
